# 📘 Lekce 5 — CRUD

## Query #1 — CRUD operace

```sql
CREATE TABLE Produkty (
    Id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Nazev NVARCHAR(50)
);

INSERT INTO Produkty
VALUES (1, 'Notebook');

UPDATE Produkty
SET Nazev = 'Herní notebook'
WHERE Id = 1;

DELETE FROM Produkty
WHERE Id = 1;
```

| CRUD   | Význam |
| ------ | ------ |
| Create | INSERT |
| Read   | SELECT |
| Update | UPDATE |
| Delete | DELETE |

