# 📘 Lekce 14 — TRANSAKCE

## COMMIT

```sql
BEGIN TRANSACTION;

UPDATE [Ucty]
SET [Balance] = [Balance] - 100
WHERE [Id] = 1;

UPDATE [Ucty]
SET [Balance] = [Balance] + 100
WHERE [Id] = 2;

COMMIT TRANSACTION;
```

---

## ROLLBACK

```sql
BEGIN TRANSACTION;

DELETE FROM [Uzivatele]
WHERE [Id] = 5;

ROLLBACK TRANSACTION;
```

👉 změna se neuloží

