# 📘 Lekce 18 — STORED PROCEDURES

## Vytvoření procedury

```sql
CREATE PROCEDURE GetUsers
AS
BEGIN
    SELECT *
    FROM [Users];
END;
```

---

## EXEC

```sql
EXEC GetUsers;
```

---

## Procedura s parametrem

```sql
CREATE PROCEDURE GetUsersByCity
    @City NVARCHAR(50)
AS
BEGIN
    SELECT *
    FROM [Users]
    WHERE [City] = @City;
END;
```

